OL,3,CConservation group warns rivers are
OL,4,Cbeing contaminated due to blocked
OL,5,Cdrains
OL,7,FEnvironmental campaigners in
OL,8,FGloucestershire are warning that
OL,9,Fblocked drains are damaging the
OL,10,Fcounty's rivers.
OL,12,FLocal people in the Cotswolds village
OL,13,Fof Sherbourne say that contaminated
OL,14,Frainwater is running off fields and
OL,15,Froads and instead of ending up in
OL,16,Fdrains, is pouring into streams and
OL,17,Frivers.
