OL,3,CConservation group warns rivers are
OL,4,Cbeing contaminated due to blocked
OL,5,Cdrains
OL,7,FOne resident, Roger Davies, has
OL,8,Fidentified a brook that runs alongside
OL,9,Fhis property, which he says is being
OL,10,Fpolluted.
OL,12,FRoger believes it is due to a blocked
OL,13,Fup ditch.
OL,15,F"This is a channel that runs under the
OL,16,Froad and to a pool that has been built
OL,17,Fdeliberately there to absorb the
OL,18,Fwater. But because it's been blocked,
OL,19,Fit carries on down the road into the
OL,20,Fbrook and then fills up the Sherbourne
OL,21,FLakes," he said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
