OL,3,CConservation group warns rivers are
OL,4,Cbeing contaminated due to blocked
OL,5,Cdrains
OL,7,F"We need to slow the water from
OL,8,Fgetting on the road, we need to feed
OL,9,Fit off the road, into ditched and into
OL,10,Fsoakaways - and that allows the silt
OL,11,Fto drop out and then it's cleaner
OL,12,Fwater going into the brook and less
OL,13,Fsilt," Roger added.
OL,15,FEnvironmental campaigners say that
OL,16,Frivers are already under strain due to
OL,17,Fsewage being released into them,
OL,18,Fmeaning the addition polluted
OL,19,Frainwater puts them under extra strain.
