OL,3,CConservation group warns rivers are
OL,4,Cbeing contaminated due to blocked
OL,5,Cdrains
OL,7,FDebbie Campbell from the Cotswold
OL,8,FRivers Trust, said: "What we have is a
OL,9,Fconstant battle, rivers are always
OL,10,Falways fighting. So, we've got sewage
OL,11,Fpollution that comes from the water
OL,12,Fcompanies, and also we've got water
OL,13,Fthat just literally comes gushing down
OL,14,Fat such a rate and it's just basically
OL,15,Fpicking up microplastics.
OL,17,F"It picks up oil and all those things
OL,18,Fand silt that all comes gushing into
OL,19,Fthe rivers. Literally, rivers have no
OL,20,Fchance."
