OL,5,Cdrains
OL,7,FA former Environment Agency worker and
OL,8,Flocal resident, Dave Throup, also
OL,9,Fagrees that agricultural runoff is
OL,10,Fproving a huge challenge for
OL,11,FGloucestershire's rivers.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, agricultural pollution
OL,14,Fis a really big problem", he said.
OL,16,F"There's a huge focus, quite rightly,
OL,17,Fon sewage pollution, but in fact
OL,18,Fthere's more water bodies affected by
OL,19,Fagricultural pollution than are by
OL,20,Fsewage.
