OL,7,F"The problem is when the rainwater
OL,8,Fruns off, it takes soil with it - it
OL,9,Ftakes nutrients with it, it takes
OL,10,Fpesticides with it, and all that is
OL,11,Fgetting into the various rivers and
OL,12,Fwater bodies."
